 <metadata>
  <name>Sherborn</name>
  <desc>A nice longer option to the south of Boston. Commuting out of the city can be a bit frustrating during rush hour but otherwise this route has some rolling hills and is completely paved.</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Tim Beaver</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/23022900"/>
